flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive Claim<br/>from User"]
    B --> C[Advocate A<br/>Argues FOR Claim]
    B --> D[Advocate B<br/>Argues AGAINST Claim]
    C --> E["Collect Both<br/>Arguments"]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Judge Reviews<br/>Both Arguments]
    F --> G[Judge Scores<br/>Each Argument]
    G --> H{Winner<br/>Determined?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Declare Winner<br/>with Reasoning]
    H -->|No| J[Judge Requests<br/>Clarification]
    J --> F
    I --> K([End])